      "content": "i don't want a chance to \"get better.\" i want the noise to stop. i want the cold to stop. everything i do just leads to more pain. wouldn't it be more peaceful if i just... stopped fighting it? if i just let the quiet take over instead of trying to force myself to endure this?",
